SalatÄƒ Boeuf

INGREDIENTS

500g Beef
150g Peas
150g Carrots
150g Parsnip
150g Celery
500g Potato
150g Pickled Peppers
150g Pickled Cucumbers
S & P
Parsley
2 egg yolks
15ml Yellow Mustard
300ml Oil
Lemon Juice


MISE

Show Peas
Dice Carrots
Dice Parsnip
Dice Celery
Chop Parsley
Dice Potato
Drain Pickled Peppers
Chop Pickled Peppers
Drain Pickled Cucumbers
Chop Pickled Cucumbers
Juice Lemon
Show Beef
Crack and separate Egg Yolks
Add Mustard
Add S & P
Add Lemon Juice
Mix
Add Oil
Mix

COOK

Medium Pot over medium high
Add water
Season with salt and pepper
Add beef
Boil for 20min
Drain and cool

Medium Pot over medium high
Add Carrots
Add Parsnip
Add Potato
Add Peas
Boil for 10min
Drain and cool

Chop Beef
Beef and Veg in bowl
Add Celery
Add Peas
Add Pickles
Add Parsley
Season with S&P
Add Mayo